Description: Fix 64-bit portability issues
 - mp3.c: use long for filelen to avoid truncation of ftell() return value
 - wavefront.c: cast fn to size_t before malloc multiplication
 - cgm.c: cast n/num to size_t before malloc/memcpy multiplication
 - mpglib/layer3.c: explicit int cast for ptrdiff_t->int narrowing in loop bounds
 - mpglib/mpglib.h: use int instead of long in struct buf/framebuf,
   consistent with interface.c usage (audio frames are always small)
Generated-by: Claude Sonnet 4.6
Reviewed-by: Nicolas HOUDELOT <nicolas@demosdebs.org>
Applied-Upstream: no
Last-Update: 2026-04-20
